Module com.example.lab23a
Package com.example.lab23a.model

Class StudyTerm

java.lang.Object
com.example.lab23a.model.StudyTerm
public class StudyTerm extends Object
StudyTerm is a pair of term and its definition. The object stores information about the pair and user's progress.
